title: LOVECRAFT COUNTRY Episode 6 Breakdown, Theories, and Details You Missed!
author: Think Story
comment: This show is a complete roller coaster ride great actors and writing.
Jamie Chung is finally getting the acting opportunity she deserves  -  and she's killing it (pun intended). She is fantastic.
I was pleasantly surprised when I heard them actually speak Korean to other Koreans. Too many times shows just have English with an accent all the way through. I appreciate this.
description:
In this video we take a deep dive, review, recap, and breakdown episode 6 "Meet Me in Daegu" of HBO's latest series Lovecraft Country based off the book by Matt Ruff. Review, recap, and easter eggs!
